'''酒石酸氢钠'''是一种有机酸盐，化学式为NaC<sub>4</sub>H<sub>5</sub>O<sub>6</sub>。它可由[[氢氧化钠|氢氧化钠]]和(+)-[[酒石酸|酒石酸]]在水中反应得到。<ref name=MH />它和[[硝酸银|硝酸银]]反应，可以得到[Ag(μ<sub>3</sub>-HC<sub>4</sub>H<sub>4</sub>O<sub>6</sub>)(H<sub>2</sub>O)]<sub>n</sub>。<ref name=MH>{{cite journal|journal=Polyhedron|volume=166|language=en|date=2019-07|pages=115–122|doi=10.1016/j.poly.2019.03.032|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0277538719302050|title=Solid–solid and solid–liquid conversion of sodium and silver nano coordination polymers|accessdate=2021-01-29|author=Maryam Hasheminezhad, Kamran Akhbari, Anukorn Phuruangrat}}</ref>

==结构==
酒石酸氢钠为[[单斜晶系|单斜晶系]]晶体，空间群''P''2<sub>1</sub>，而钾、铷、铯的酒石酸氢盐的空间群为''P''2<sub>1</sub>2<sub>1</sub>2<sub>1</sub>。其结构中存在L-酒石酸氢根离子间的不对称O–H…O氢键。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica Section C Crystal Structure Communications|volume=52|issue=8|date=1996-08-15|pages=1948–1950|doi=10.1107/S0108270196005288|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270196005288|title=Sodium Hydrogen L-Tartrate|accessdate=2021-01-29|author=S. Matsumoto, S. Kashino|archive-date=2020-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222231834/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270196005288|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|issue=10|doi=10.1524/zkri.1994.209.10.803|title=Structures of the hydrogen (+)-tartrates of sodium, thallium(I) and silver(I)|volume=209|journal=Zeitschrift für Kristallographie - Crystalline Materials|date=1994-01-01|url=http://dx.doi.org/10.1524/zkri.1994.209.10.803|issn=2194-4946|author=R. C. Bott, G. Smith, D. S. Sagatys, D. E. Lynch, A. N. Reddy, H. L. Kennard|accessdate=2021-01-29}}</ref>

酒石酸氢钠的一水合物为[[正交晶系|正交晶系]]晶体，空间群''P''2<sub>1</sub>2<sub>1</sub>2<sub>1</sub><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Acta Crystallographica Section C Crystal Structure Communications|volume=49|issue=6|date=1993-06-15|pages=1150–1152|doi=10.1107/S0108270192012605|url=http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270192012605|title=Structure of sodium hydrogen (+)-tartrate monohydrate|accessdate=2021-01-29|author=R. C. Bott, D. S. Sagatys, D. E. Lynch, G. Smith, C. H. L. Kennard|archive-date=2018-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180603175237/http://scripts.iucr.org/cgi-bin/paper?S0108270192012605|dead-url=no}}</ref>；一水合物的另一种单斜''P''2<sub>1</sub>/''c''晶型也是已知的。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Crystallography Reports|volume=60|issue=1|language=en|issn=1063-7745|date=2015-01|pages=72–74|doi=10.1134/S1063774515010265|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1134/S1063774515010265|title=Crystal structure of monobasic sodium tartrate monohydrate|accessdate=2021-01-29|author=E. K. Titaeva, N. V. Somov, V. N. Portnov, D. N. Titaev}}</ref>
